ed="T" n="0877b27"/><persName key="A013708">釋文瓚</persName>，姓<name>張</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000003796">晉陽</placeName>人也。天姿整恪，幼事<lb
ed="T" n="0877b28"/>師於<placeName key="PL000000003781"><placeName>并州</placeName><placeName>崇福寺</placeName></placeName>。學該群籍，控帶<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2124"/>三乘。至<lb
ed="T" n="0877b29"/>若金版銀繩之籙，龍韜象祕之文，罔不耰<pb ed="T" n="0877c" xml:id="T50.2061.0877c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0877c01"/>耘<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2125"/>情田，波濤口海，宣暢皇化，對揚天休<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2126"/>，一<lb
ed="T" n="0877c02"/>皆悅服。詔為翻譯，并<placeName key="PL000000023657"><placeName>河南</placeName><placeName>佛授記寺</placeName></placeName>兼<placeName key="PL000000042147"><placeName>京兆</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0877c03"/><placeName>安國</placeName></placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000042150">荷恩</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000042324">崇福</placeName>等寺大德。好修福事，設無遮<ptr type="glossary" target="#g379"/><lb
ed="T" n="0877c04"/>一百會，凡聖混淆，一皆等施。縱風雲連起，及<lb
ed="T" n="0877c05"/>至齋日，必晴明晏然，感動人祇，福無唐<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1646"/>設。<lb
ed="T" n="0877c06"/>春秋六十餘，卒於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042150">本院</ref>。境內苦霧如泣，數<lb
ed="T" n="0877c07"/>日不解焉。</p>
